      "role": "user",
      "content": "grounding doesn't work for a ghost. i'm just going through the motions. i wake up, i pretend, i go to work, i sleep. it's just a loop of nothingness. it feels so pointless to keep the performance going when the actor is already dead inside. why do i even bother keeping up the charade?",
