    "summary": "The user expresses profound feelings of dissociation, depersonalization, and existential emptiness, describing themselves as a \"hollow shell\" or a \"ghost.\" The assistant responds with empathy, validates the intensity and exhaustion of the user's feelings, and provides grounding techniques and encouragement to seek help/survival.",
